data.description: Walk into this fairytale home surrounded by personality that you can only image from a story book. Walk into this home through the ornate double entry. This 3 bedroom ranch style home has a kitchen that is designed to showcase the beautiful wood beams throughout. When you stroll through the home notice the little details in the doors, the ornate fireplace, custom vanity and much much more. Not only are you located with in the city but the charming backyard is where you can sit and enjoy the coy pond or grow your own garden. With plenty of space this property also includes 2 storage sheds to store your outdoor equipment and frees up the extra long garage to continue using it as a craftsman or auto workshop. This interesting home has little surprises in every little corner including a laundry shoot and build in hidden wall safe. Not only is this home a relaxing oasis, it is also energy efficient with the newly installed solar panels. Appliances stay with the home and many new upgrades have been done for you. You have to see this one for yourself.
